flows.func:
const { supersonic } = inputs;
await supersonic.api.auth.removeSession();

const {
  message,
  duration,
  position,
  animation,
  shadow,
  backgroundColor,
  shadowColor,
  textColor,
  opacity,
  hideOnPress,
  supersonic,
} = inputs;

await supersonic.api.toast.show({
  message,
  duration,
  position,
  animation,
  shadow,
  backgroundColor,
  shadowColor,
  textColor,
  opacity,
  hideOnPress,
});

const { supersonic } = inputs;
await supersonic.api.navigation.replaceToInit();

A negative number represents the distance from the bottom of screen.

A positive number represents the distance form the top of screen.

0 will position the toast to the middle of screen.
